Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: MovieTorrentParser
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Handy movie torrent parser
Home-page: UNKNOWN
Author: mcharbit
Author-email: mcharbit@pentalog.fr
License: GPL
Description: Handy parser going through RSS provided by torrent sites, selecting movies with proper encoding and IMDB rating,
        retrieving other useful info from IMDb and sending a digest by mail
        
        Usage :
        
            python parser.py [ name_of_your_config_file ] [ -l log_file ]
        
        If config_file is not passed, MovieTorrentParser will prompt you for the settings, let you save them to a file for future use, and let you schedule an automatic run of the script
        
        If -l option is passed, logs are written to log_file, printed to stdout otherwise
Platform: UNKNOWN
